<s> WCAG says that the names have to be clear enough to make it obvious what is happening.  </s>
<s> "nav" is not obvious, but "site navigation" or is more so.  </s>
<s> The name attribute can not include spaces, so in many cases you will want to use a title attribute (you are writing for people to read, where french may not be their first language - avoid being  </s>
<s> cryptic - which is a P1 checkpoint).  </s>
<s> But I can't see anything in WCAG that makes it compulsory to use the title attribute.  </s>
