<s> The wording is 'title', but I interpret it to mean using the name attribute as well.  </s>
<s> Surely we should do both.  </s>
<s> I know JAWS uses the name, but the name of an element is not really intended for human consumption, but for the browser.  </s>
<s> I think this is analogous to the way that when an image has no ALT text, JAWS reads out the filename.  </s>
<s> It was the best it could do in the early days, before titles and alt text.  </s>
<s> 12.1 Title each frame to facilitate frame identification and navigation.  </s>
<s> [Priority 1] For example, in HTML use the "title" attribute on FRAME elements.  </s>
